msgid ""
"The WordPress Abilities API REST routes must be available before third-party\n"
"provider plugins or external clients can discover and run abilities."
msgstr "在第三方 provider 插件或外部客户端发现并运行 abilities 之前，WordPress Abilities API REST routes 必须可用。"

#. Found in description header.
msgid "Third-Party Integration Quickstart"
msgstr "第三方集成快速开始"

#. Screenshot description.
msgid "Developer Access tab with copyable REST endpoint values, raw discovery fetches, and ability ID export."
msgstr "Developer Access tab，包含可复制的 REST endpoint 值、raw discovery fetch 和 ability ID export。"

#. Screenshot description.
msgid "Safe Checks tab explaining what each check proves before showing summary results and raw response support details."
msgstr "Safe Checks tab，在显示 summary results 和 raw response support details 之前，说明每个检查证明什么。"

#. Screenshot description.
msgid "Available Abilities catalog with filters, risk grouping, availability, and technical details for support."
msgstr "Available Abilities catalog，包含筛选、风险分组、可用性和用于支持排查的技术细节。"

#. Screenshot description.
msgid "Site ability status overview with available ability count, write safeguards, host detection, and next actions."
msgstr "站点 ability 状态概览，包含可用 ability 数量、写入保护、host 检测和下一步操作。"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<code>npcink_abilities_toolkit_get_workflow_definitions()</code>"
msgstr "<code>npcink_abilities_toolkit_get_workflow_definitions()</code>"

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<code>npcink_abilities_toolkit_get_registered()</code>"
msgstr "<code>npcink_abilities_toolkit_get_registered()</code>"

#. Found in description header.
msgid "Developer Verification"
msgstr "开发者验证"

#. Found in description header.
msgid "Admin Page"
msgstr "后台页面"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "For isolated bounded-chain performance validation, run:"
msgstr "如需隔离验证有边界链路性能："

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "When the plugin is installed in a local WordPress site, run:"
msgstr "当插件安装在本地 WordPress 站点中时："

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "Core governance handoff docs include a catalog snapshot, permission matrix, and schema boundary audit for hosts that consume this plugin through <code>npcink-ai-core</code>."
msgstr ""
"Core governance handoff 文档包含 catalog snapshot、permission matrix 和 schema boundary audit，供通过 <code>npcink-ai-core</code> 消费本插件的 host 使用。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "It also includes <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/list-workflow-recipes</code> and <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/get-workflow-recipe</code>, read-only host composition recipe metadata discovery abilities. These expose metadata only and do not execute workflow runtime behavior."
msgstr ""
"它也包含 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/list-workflow-recipes</code> 和 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/get-workflow-recipe</code>，这是只读的 host composition recipe metadata discovery abilities。它们只暴露 metadata，不执行 workflow runtime behavior。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "It also includes <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/search-posts</code> and <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/search-post-meta</code>, bounded local WordPress search helpers for keyword and explicit post-meta discovery. These are read-only helpers and do not call external search indexes or mutate content."
msgstr ""
"它也包含 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/search-posts</code> 和 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/search-post-meta</code>，用于 keyword 和明确 post-meta discovery 的有边界本地 WordPress search helpers。这些都是只读 helper，不会调用外部 search index，也不会修改内容。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "It also includes <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/wp-diagnostics-summary</code>, a redacted WordPress-only diagnostics summary for Abilities API clients. This summary intentionally omits Npcink AI settings, MCP settings, API keys, database names, table prefixes, filesystem paths, error logs, and external HTTP probes."
msgstr ""
"它也包含 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/wp-diagnostics-summary</code>，这是面向 Abilities API client 的、只包含 WordPress 信息的 redacted diagnostics summary。该摘要会有意省略 Npcink AI 设置、MCP 设置、API keys、数据库名、table prefix、filesystem paths、error logs 和 external HTTP probes。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "The plugin includes migrated low-risk WordPress read abilities, deterministic comment helpers, and host-governed WordPress write/destructive abilities using canonical <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/*</code> ids."
msgstr ""
"插件包含迁移后的低风险 WordPress read abilities、确定性的 comment helpers，以及使用规范 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/*</code> ids 的 host-governed WordPress write/destructive abilities。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "After activation with a Npcink AI host plugin, open Npcink AI -&gt; AI Ability Set in wp-admin. When this standalone package is installed without a Npcink AI host menu, open Tools -&gt; AI Ability Set instead."
msgstr ""
"与 Npcink AI host 插件一起启用后，在 wp-admin 中打开 Npcink AI -&gt; AI Ability Set。单独安装本包且没有 Npcink AI host 菜单时，打开 Tools -&gt; AI Ability Set。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "The <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/upload-media-from-url</code> ability can download a media file from a URL provided by an authenticated caller when an approved host runtime commits that ability. In that case WordPress sends an HTTP request to the caller-provided URL in order to fetch the media file for the local media library. The remote endpoint is chosen by the caller, not by this plugin."
msgstr ""
"<code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/upload-media-from-url</code> ability 可以在已审批的 host runtime commit 该 ability 时，从已认证调用方提供的 URL 下载媒体文件。在这种情况下，WordPress 会向调用方提供的 URL 发送 HTTP 请求，以便把媒体文件获取到本地媒体库。远程端点由调用方选择，不由本插件选择。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "Some abilities can prepare request payloads for a separate host or cloud add-on, but this plugin does not send those payloads to an external service by itself."
msgstr "部分 abilities 可以为独立的 host 或 cloud add-on 准备请求 payload，但这个插件本身不会把这些 payload 发送到外部服务。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "This plugin does not automatically contact Npcink AI, model providers, analytics services, tracking services, or cloud services."
msgstr "这个插件不会自动联系 Npcink AI、模型提供商、分析服务、追踪服务或云服务。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "Host composition recipe metadata is available through read-only helpers and Abilities API discovery abilities for hosts that need catalog discovery without execution ownership."
msgstr ""
"Host composition recipe metadata 通过只读 helper 和 Abilities API discovery abilities 提供给需要 catalog discovery、但不需要执行所有权的 host。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "Read-only host composition recipe metadata may document how hosts can compose abilities, but those records do not run queues, schedule jobs, execute workflows, or create a second registry."
msgstr "只读的 host composition recipe metadata 可以记录 host 如何组合 abilities，但这些记录不会运行队列、调度任务、执行 workflow，也不会创建第二套 registry。"

#. Found in description paragraph.
msgid "It can be used by any WordPress plugin or client that consumes the WordPress Abilities API. Npcink AI is one optional consumer, not the owner of this plugin."
msgstr "任何消费 WordPress Abilities API 的 WordPress 插件或客户端都可以使用它。Npcink AI 是一个可选消费者，并不是这个插件的所有者。"

