#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Documented the foundation-layer testing strategy and default local source gate."
msgstr "记录 foundation-layer testing strategy 和默认本地 source gate。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Upgraded GitHub Actions checkout to the Node 24-compatible <code>actions/checkout@v5</code>."
msgstr "将 GitHub Actions checkout 升级到兼容 Node 24 的 <code>actions/checkout@v5</code>。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Published the canonical public GitHub repository and documented the post-publication gate baseline."
msgstr "发布规范的公开 GitHub 仓库，并记录 post-publication gate baseline。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Aligned CI and PHPStan with the package PHP 8.0 runtime floor."
msgstr "让 CI 和 PHPStan 对齐 package 的 PHP 8.0 runtime floor。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Added Composer dependency advisory audit to the default local and CI source gate."
msgstr "为默认本地和 CI source gate 添加 Composer dependency advisory audit。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Expanded acceptance contracts and first-party pack documentation for the new handoff artifacts."
msgstr "为新的 handoff artifacts 扩展 acceptance contracts 和 first-party pack documentation。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Kept candidate review helpers suggestion-only and host-governed; they do not create proposals, approve work, execute writes, or contact external providers."
msgstr ""
"保持 candidate review helpers 为 suggestion-only 和 host-governed；它们不会创建 proposals、approve work、execute writes 或 contact external providers。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Added read-only review artifacts for image candidates, internal link candidates, taxonomy suggestions, and comment reply suggestions."
msgstr "添加 image candidates、internal link candidates、taxonomy suggestions 和 comment reply suggestions 的只读 review artifacts。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Initial standalone release."
msgstr "初始 standalone release。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Verified Npcink AI catalog compatibility against a WordPress site."
msgstr "基于 WordPress 站点验证 Npcink AI catalog compatibility。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Established <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/*</code> as the canonical id namespace for abilities owned by this plugin."
msgstr "将 <code>npcink-abilities-toolkit/*</code> 确立为本插件拥有 abilities 的规范 id namespace。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Expanded REST verification coverage for governance metadata and schemas."
msgstr "扩展 governance metadata 和 schemas 的 REST verification coverage。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Hardened media replacement and Cloud derivative adoption previews so approved replacements can repair exact post-content media URLs, including old intermediate-size URLs."
msgstr ""
"强化 media replacement 和 Cloud derivative adoption previews，使已审批 replacement 可以修复精确 post-content media URLs，包括旧 intermediate-size URLs。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Added taxonomy assignment proposal support and strengthened Core consumer handoff checks for harvested workflow surfaces."
msgstr "添加 taxonomy assignment proposal support，并加强 harvested workflow surfaces 的 Core consumer handoff checks。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Renamed nonproduction cleanup abilities and media cleanup inputs to avoid public <code>test</code> terminology in released ability ids and schema fields."
msgstr "重命名非生产 cleanup abilities 和 media cleanup inputs，避免 released ability ids 和 schema fields 中出现公开 <code>test</code> 术语。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Removed development demo ability controls from the admin page and kept showcase, model-call, write, and workflow execution outside this package surface."
msgstr "从后台页面移除 development demo ability controls，并把 showcase、model-call、write 和 workflow execution 留在本包 surface 之外。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Added bundled translation templates and eight starter locale packs for the admin connection/discovery surface, API ability labels/descriptions, and common runtime error messages."
msgstr ""
"添加 bundled translation templates 和八个 starter locale packs，覆盖后台 connection/discovery surface、API ability labels/descriptions 和常见 runtime error messages。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
#, gp-priority: low
msgid "Improved the admin page as a connection and discovery surface with clearer package status, catalog navigation, copyable REST endpoints, and two bounded read-only checks."
msgstr "改进后台页面，让它成为更清晰的 connection 和 discovery surface，包含 package status、catalog navigation、可复制 REST endpoints 和两个有边界的只读 checks。"

#. Found in changelog list item.
